1
00:00:00,834 --> 00:00:02,419
Teacher.

2
00:00:03,670 --> 00:00:05,964
You're spacing out again, aren't you?

3
00:00:07,924 --> 00:00:09,718
You said you have someone you like, right?

4
00:00:13,388 --> 00:00:13,805
Yeah.

5
00:00:14,556 --> 00:00:16,307
So focus on the lesson.

6
00:00:18,101 --> 00:00:20,228
But there was someone else next to him.

7
00:00:20,228 --> 00:00:22,105
Do you still like him even after that?

8
00:00:22,605 --> 00:00:25,233
I don't know what you're talking about.

9
00:00:25,608 --> 00:00:27,485
I saw everything.

10
00:00:27,652 --> 00:00:30,030
You getting rejected...

11
00:00:30,030 --> 00:00:32,032
And that person having someone else by his side...

12
00:00:40,540 --> 00:00:42,751
What are you trying to say?

13
00:00:46,254 --> 00:00:48,423
I like you, Teacher.

14
00:01:15,533 --> 00:01:16,826
What is this?

15
00:01:16,993 --> 00:01:18,536
A kid like you shouldn't smoke...

16
00:01:18,745 --> 00:01:20,371
I'm an adult.

17
00:01:20,371 --> 00:01:21,831
I'm allowed to smoke.

18
00:01:22,665 --> 00:01:24,834
How did you even know I was here?

19
00:01:25,752 --> 00:01:26,961
Why?

20
00:01:26,961 --> 00:01:29,255
Are you afraid I'd follow you around everywhere?

21
00:01:36,971 --> 00:01:38,014
Hey, Haemin.

22
00:01:38,223 --> 00:01:40,350
Where are you?

23
00:01:40,850 --> 00:01:41,851
Over here.

24
00:01:49,150 --> 00:01:50,985
It's bad for your health.

25
00:01:50,985 --> 00:01:54,239
Plus, I'm a non-smoker, so kissing a smoker...

26
00:01:54,239 --> 00:01:57,742
Is kind of a turn-off.

27
00:02:09,587 --> 00:02:11,548
Ugh, so annoying.

28
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:13,174
Why did you want to meet outside?

29
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:15,468
I came to see Teacher.

30
00:02:18,096 --> 00:02:19,305
Unbelievable.

31
00:02:20,056 --> 00:02:22,016
What's so unbelievable about it?

32
00:02:22,016 --> 00:02:23,601
The weather's nice.

33
00:02:27,689 --> 00:02:29,983
But do you think he'll notice us?

34
00:02:30,275 --> 00:02:31,359
Notice who?

35
00:02:31,359 --> 00:02:33,194
You?

36
00:02:33,194 --> 00:02:33,862
Me?

37
00:02:34,070 --> 00:02:35,905
Well, I kept pulling him in,

38
00:02:35,905 --> 00:02:37,699
but he wasn't budging,

39
00:02:37,699 --> 00:02:38,992
so I used you a little bit.

40
00:02:40,952 --> 00:02:42,495
Do you really think this will work?

41
00:02:43,788 --> 00:02:44,789
Then what else can I do?

42
00:02:44,789 --> 00:02:46,624
I have to try something.

43
00:02:46,958 --> 00:02:48,543
Right?

44
00:02:58,136 --> 00:03:02,056
I'm not the right person for you, Jaeon.

45
00:03:26,956 --> 00:03:31,002
(Jaeon's past message asking to come see him)

46
00:03:38,176 --> 00:03:40,553
He's quiet today.

47
00:03:40,553 --> 00:03:43,473
He usually would be blowing up my phone.

48
00:03:44,724 --> 00:03:46,017
Or maybe...

49
00:03:46,017 --> 00:03:48,102
Did he come to see me?

50
00:03:59,447 --> 00:04:04,994
Why do I keep caring about him?

51
00:04:12,252 --> 00:04:17,006
Ah, right. The welcome party.

52
00:04:28,184 --> 00:04:30,061
Hey.

53
00:04:30,061 --> 00:04:32,522
Hey, pull yourself together.

54
00:04:32,522 --> 00:04:33,982
It's just you and me left.

55
00:04:33,982 --> 00:04:35,650
Ah, whatever.

56
00:04:41,364 --> 00:04:42,156
Huh?

57
00:04:42,949 --> 00:04:44,659
Professor?

58
00:04:44,826 --> 00:04:46,577
You're still here?

59
00:04:48,955 --> 00:04:50,999
You look pretty drunk yourself.

60
00:04:50,999 --> 00:04:52,542
Leave Jaeon with me and go.

61
00:04:55,003 --> 00:04:56,546
But still...

62
00:05:01,050 --> 00:05:04,429
Then please take care of him.

63
00:05:10,518 --> 00:05:11,644
Yoon Jaeon.

64
00:05:18,943 --> 00:05:20,611
Teacher.

65
00:05:20,611 --> 00:05:21,779
Oh, wait.

66
00:05:21,779 --> 00:05:22,655
Professor.

67
00:05:23,072 --> 00:05:25,325
Greetings.

68
00:05:26,701 --> 00:05:29,120
Walk straight.

69
00:05:29,996 --> 00:05:32,540
I can't walk.

70
00:05:32,540 --> 00:05:35,918
My legs are giving out.

71
00:05:39,630 --> 00:05:41,507
Let's go.

72
00:05:52,143 --> 00:05:54,228
Go inside and lie down.

73
00:05:54,937 --> 00:05:55,980
I don't want to.

74
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:57,982
I like it here.

75
00:06:05,073 --> 00:06:07,533
Teacher...

76
00:06:08,034 --> 00:06:09,619
Yeah.

77
00:06:09,994 --> 00:06:13,873
Just like I promised you,

78
00:06:13,873 --> 00:06:16,459
I studied really hard,

79
00:06:16,459 --> 00:06:18,795
and got into college too.

80
00:06:20,630 --> 00:06:22,632
Good job.

81
00:06:26,886 --> 00:06:29,305
Let go of me.

82
00:06:38,231 --> 00:06:40,900
You said you'd grant my wish.

83
00:06:44,695 --> 00:06:49,325
Can you kiss me?

84
00:06:49,700 --> 00:06:52,078
Enough with the drunken nonsense.

85
00:06:52,078 --> 00:06:53,496
Don't do something you'll regret.

86
00:06:54,205 --> 00:06:55,915
I mean it, though.

87
00:06:57,542 --> 00:07:01,796
If you do, I won't bother you anymore.

88
00:07:01,838 --> 00:07:06,592
If you grant my wish, I'll do whatever you tell me to.

89
00:07:07,176 --> 00:07:09,762
You know I always listen to you.

90
00:07:14,267 --> 00:07:16,227
You're promising me.

91
00:07:17,061 --> 00:07:18,980
That you'll do exactly as I say.

92
00:07:32,076 --> 00:07:33,119
What was that?

93
00:07:34,370 --> 00:07:36,831
I'm not a kid.

94
00:07:37,165 --> 00:07:40,001
I can at least tell the difference between a peck and a kiss.
